snippet.title: Quake Map Jam 8 Film Noir with special effects
snippet.description:
Quake; Added film grain & scratch effects for the Film Noir themed Map Jam 8. Both effects can be used individually or together.
Using the SMC feature to achieve it. Adjust the intensity to your personal liking; I used a more intense value to better see it in the clip.
Download: http://quakeone.com/forum/quake-mod-releases/finished-works/6241-small-mod-compilation
